cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.IT, cs.DS, cs.SI

This paper discusses a method for improving the privacy and accuracy of distributed machine learning algorithms using ADMM. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as privacy is a key concern. The paper also involves optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper proposes a modified ADMM algorithm, which could be relevant to cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
